        "richtext_t7PU3Q": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>To celebrate World Book Day, we’re pledging mini school packs to <strong>five</strong> schools across <strong>five</strong> regions in the <strong>UK</strong>. These packs offer a fantastic new tool for literacy development, perfect for use in the classroom or for creating listening stations in your school library.</p><p>But we need your help! We’re looking for nominations, and we’d love to hear about your school’s commitment to literacy, both within the school and throughout the wider community.</p><p>We also want to hear from schools that are passionate about literacy but are facing challenges, whether it’s obstacles or a lack of funding, that make it difficult to grow their literacy initiatives.</p><p>It’s easy, just fill out the short application form below (it takes less than five minutes).</p><p>A panel of Voxblock team members and industry peers will review the submissions and select a winner for each region.</p><p><strong>Regions:</strong> Scotland, North England, South England, Wales and Northern Ireland</p><p><strong>Deadline:</strong> 23:59 on <strong>31st March</strong></p><p><strong>Who can apply:</strong> Everyone! Whether you’re a teacher, headteacher, or a parent, we’d love to hear from you.</p><p><a href=\"https://voxblock.co.uk/pages/competition-t-cs?_pos=1&_psq=comp&_ss=e&_v=1.0\" title=\"https://voxblock.co.uk/pages/competition-t-cs?_pos=1&_psq=comp&_ss=e&_v=1.0\">View all Terms and Conditions and judging criteria here.</a></p>"
